article.headline: UC Santa Barbara 90, Vanguard 63
article.story: SANTA BARBARA, Calif. (AP) -- Chris Devine had 22 points and 11 rebounds and Alex Harris had 18 points and six assists to lead UC Santa Barbara past Vanguard 90-63 on Tuesday night. Devine went 10-for-13 from the field, Harris went 8-for-13 and the Gauchos (8-2) shot 62.5 percent as a team to win their fourth straight. Dennis Heenan led Vanguard (2-8) with 18 points. He made four of seven from 3-point range.
